soccer.common

Class TOS_Constants

  • java.lang.Object
    • soccer.common.Game_Constants
      • soccer.common.TOS_Constants
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Field_Constants, TOS_AgentConstants

    public class TOS_Constants
extends Game_Constants
implements Field_Constants, TOS_AgentConstants
    This interface must be the only place for keeping all TOS project-wide constants. (Also see the super class and implemented interfaces.) Using locally defined public static constants in other classes is still allowed, but not recommended.
    Author:
    vkyrylov (2010)
